To do a drop punch record in [[Pro Tools]] set the record mode to [[Pro Tools:punch in record|Quickpunch or Trackpunch]] and add some [[Pro_Tools:Pre_roll_and_post_roll_setting|pre roll and post roll time]].Then make a time line selection encompassing where you want the recording to begin and push record. 

